summary: This is a declaration by a custodian of records certifying compliance with a grand jury subpoena dated June 14, 2019, issued by Assistant United States Attorney Alison Moe. The custodian attests that the provided records were made and kept in the regular course of business.

persons.name: Alison Moe
persons.context: Signed the grand jury subpoena dated June 14, 2019, for which this custodian declaration is providing records.

events.title: Grand Jury Subpoena Issued
events.description: A grand jury subpoena was issued and signed by Assistant United States Attorney Alison Moe, requesting specified records from a business.

keyFacts: A grand jury subpoena was issued on June 14, 2019, by Assistant U.S. Attorney Alison Moe as part of an investigation.
A custodian of records for an unspecified business has certified and provided records in response to the subpoena.
The custodian declares the records were made and kept in the regular course of business, meeting federal evidence rules.
The document is part of the evidence tracking system with identifiers SDNY_GM_00004724, EFTA_00118797, and EFTA01265482.
